        <initializer>= false</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Use unwrapped positions for moment computation. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>When true, positions are computed as: x_unwrap = x + wrapX * Lx</para>
<para>Requires <ref refid="structpar2_1_1ParticlesView" kindref="compound">ParticlesView</ref> to have wrapX/Y/Z set. Essential for correct statistics under periodic BC.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>If wrapX/Y/Z are nullptr, this flag is ignored. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
